cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.CL 

This paper deals with transfer learning in Deep Reinforcement Learning (DRL) agents, which involves learning useful representations of environment states and policies. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves image processing and natural language processing, which are covered by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) respectively, making them less likely but still possible sub-categories.
